spec_data.Name: libcurl-minimal
spec_data.Description:
This is a replacement of the 'libcurl' package for minimal installations.  It
comes with a limited set of features compared to the 'libcurl' package.  On the
other hand, the package is smaller and requires fewer run-time dependencies to
be installed.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 23 Oct 2017 07:09:21 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Conservatively configured build of libcurl for minimal installations
